{"ast":null,"code":"export default {\n  name: 'AboutSection',\n  props: {\n    firstImage: {\n      type: String,\n      default: ''\n    },\n    isEnglish: {\n      type: Boolean,\n      default: false\n    }\n  }\n};","map":{"version":3,"names":["name","props","firstImage","type","String","default","isEnglish","Boolean"],"sources":["/Users/linhankuan/fvl2025/src/components/AboutSection.vue"],"sourcesContent":["<template>\n  <section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n    <div class=\"container\" style=\"background-color: #fff;padding: 30px 30px 10px;\">\n      <div class=\"about-content\">\n        <div class=\"about-text\">\n          <h2>{{ isEnglish ? 'Future Vision Lab: The Birth of a Sphere' : '未來視覺實驗室：一顆球的誕生' }}</h2>\n          <p>{{ isEnglish ? 'This is how DOME began.' : 'DOME 的開始是這樣的。' }}</p>\n          <p>{{ isEnglish ? \n            'With the relocation of the Air Force Headquarters to Dazhi, the prime location at the intersection of Jianguo South Road and Ren\\'ai Road—developed during the Japanese era and now flanked by luxury residences—was taken over by the Ministry of Culture in 2018 and transformed into a cultural experimentation base, launching the Taiwan Contemporary Culture Lab (C-LAB). In 2020, as part of C-LAB, the Taiwan Sound Lab responded to the policy of “removing the walls and opening up the site,” leading to the founding of Future Vision Lab. We began to explore the direction of technological media experiments, and our focus eventually turned to the then-popular VR, which inspired the start of the FUTURE VISION LAB project with the goal of achieving “glasses-free VR.”' : \n            '隨著空軍總部遷址大直，建國南路與仁愛路交會處這塊日治時代便開發、如今左帝寶右吾疆的精華地點，2018 年由文化部接手改造成文化實驗基地啟動臺灣當代文化實驗場（C-LAB）。而在 2020 年身為 C-LAB 一員的科技媒體實驗平台響應「卸下圍牆，打開空總」政策，未來視覺實驗室也在此時成立，同時思考科技媒體實驗該往哪些方向發展，那目光兜兜繞繞，落在彼時盛行的 VR 科技藝術，而以「裸眼 VR」為目標的 FUTURE VISION LAB 計劃因應啟動。' }}</p>\n          <p>{{ isEnglish ? \n            'When thinking of VR, one typically imagines individuals wearing headsets, each immersed in a personal world. But for the R&D planning team at the Future Vision Lab, the idea was: What if we could build a space where everyone could experience VR-like effects with the naked eye—together? “Fifty people in the same space, without devices, collectively perceiving stereoscopic visuals and sound—the sensory experience is fundamentally different.” The immersive spherical environment eliminates the boundary between the screen and the viewer, and when one lies down on the floor, the loss of spatial perception can create an illusion of falling into the image.' : \n            '想到 VR 技術，浮上眼前是每個人各自套上頭盔設備，漂浮於個體的世界。但是對 C-LAB 科技媒體實驗平台研發企劃組蔡奇宏主任來說，如果可以搭造一個空間，讓大家裸眼就能看到 VR 效果，創造集體的共享就太好了。「五十個人在同一空間裡面觀看，不需依賴設備，卻又可同時感受 VR 帶來的立體視覺效果或聲音，感官體驗是不一樣的。」 蔡奇宏解釋，傳統電影平面且鏡框的形式，多少和觀眾拉出一段距離，然而球型空間的包覆性則讓人們對於邊界的感知消失，特別是當人們躺臥在地板時，失去當下對於空間的感受或是平衡感，容易產生落入影像的錯覺。' }}</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about-stats\">\n          <img :src=\"'https://unzip-clab-api.clab.org.tw/'+ firstImage\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</template>\n\n<script>\nexport default {\n  name: 'AboutSection',\n  props: {\n    firstImage: {\n      type: String,\n      default: ''\n    },\n    isEnglish: {\n      type: Boolean,\n      default: false\n    }\n  }\n}\n</script>\n\n<style lang=\"scss\" scoped>\n.about {\n  background: #fff;\n  color: #111;\n}\n\n.container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 30px 20px 120px;\n  color: #fff;\n}\n\n.about-content {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n  gap: 50px;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\n.about-text p {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n  line-height: 1.8;\n  color: #111;\n}\n\n.about-text h2 {\n  color: #111;\n}\n\n.about-stats {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: 30px;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .about-content {\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    gap: 30px;\n  }\n}\n</style> "],"mappings":"AAuBA,eAAe;EACbA,IAAI,EAAE,cAAc;EACpBC,KAAK,EAAE;IACLC,UAAU,EAAE;MACVC,IAAI,EAAEC,MAAM;MACZC,OAAO,EAAE;IACX,CAAC;IACDC,SAAS,EAAE;MACTH,IAAI,EAAEI,OAAO;MACbF,OAAO,EAAE;IACX;EACF;AACF","ignoreList":[]},"metadata":{},"sourceType":"module","externalDependencies":[]}